metadata.name: The Morning Show
metadata.description:
Introducing my latest creation, a powerful hymn to Web 3! 
This provocative yet playful image serves as a strong tribute to the Good Morning spirit, presented like a captivating morning newscast: "The Morning Show". 
This image is meant to provoke thought, with a blend of simplicity,  and impactful. It aims to convey lightness in a chaotic world, prompting us to reflect on our contradictions. 
Originally a 1/1 piece, I now realize it's the perfect fit for an Open Edition!  
So I made two different versions of this shot:  
"The Morning Show" 1/1 (NAKED) and "The Morning Show" OE
